body:
It looks like I forgot to internalize the "_PV_SWHsurface" input (dummySurface). I apologize for that.
I managed to open your .gh file (took it 14 minutes) and to edit it.
Check the parts which are grouped in red color (there are two of them). I did a test with only 12 surfaces, to lower the waiting time.
If you can not lower the number of 1600 surfaces, prepare for some long hours of calculation.
